title: Grateful Dead Live at Hartford Civic Center on 1990-03-19
lineage: Dat > Sony PCM r500 > Tascam DA-3000 > wav 16/48
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket, Bertha, We Can Run But We Can't Hide, Jack A Roe, Picasso Moon, Brown Eyed Women, It's All Over Now, Deal

Set 2

Box Of Rain, Foolish Heart-> Playin' In The Band-> Eyes Of The World-> Jam-> Drums-> Jam-> China Doll-> Gimme Some Lovin'-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Around & Around, E: Brokedown Palace

FM Broadcast WHCN- Hartford
